  <brief_title>A New EBV Related Technologies of T Cells in Treating Malignant Tumors and Clinical Application</brief_title>
  <official_title>A New Efficient EBV AssociatedTechnologies of T Cells in Treating Malignant Tumors and Clinical Application</official_title>
  <sponsors>
